{"tid":1793962,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"想講好耐，唔好再食元朗田中！","createTime":"2019-12-22T18:17:04.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-23T10:12:27.000Z","uid":153880,"like":18,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"32a5ded98894df98c761ca99d7130dfc0605d31a","tid":1793962,"uid":153880,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-22T18:17:04.000Z","msg":"話說半年前<br />\n下午12點佢開舖嘅時候我同男友就去咗做第一個食客<br />\n嗌左個魚生飯(好似係)<br />\n一食 個帶子臭撚到我即刻lur返<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但其他都食晒... GG...<br />\n<br />\n就嗰晚同第二日我痾左十幾二十次 <br />\n好啦痾清晒 但係<br />\n我男友就感冒 腸胃炎但屙唔晒食左止瀉藥<br />\n<br />\n過左一個星期<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">佢屎窟生左個雞蛋咁大嘅野<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n睇醫生原來有細菌入左去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span><br />\n搞到要入急症室開刀抽晒啲濃佢 痛撚到PK <br />\n<br />\n有打過去1823投訴 佢搵人check左話d魚生冇問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n而家仲有少少腫 但已經唔痛<br />\n<br />\n大家慎防呢間田中 以免中招<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/beg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7dead7f72bbbb13b3bea831488676172e7b7f827","tid":1793962,"uid":321674,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-22T18:17:51.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"ea30086c184144a6297f259d5ebd2f910815ccb7","tid":1793962,"uid":210087,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-22T18:19:14.000Z","msg":"咁恐怖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9ddb506fdafd0d7b0a75c5fdb86b731ccd7a0e27","tid":1793962,"uid":311583,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-22T18:19:38.000Z","msg":"想食好野緊係嚟灣仔la, 聽日稅局見<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n【核彈】呢個方法可以防水炮車【行動po求推】<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1778898\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1778898</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【置頂】【行動po求推】好㷫呀！警曱向人群舉槍，聽日同我即刻行動。而嚟緊嘅行動係1223stuck稅局<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1793389\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1793389</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/CgxvfDH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCgxvfDH.jpg&h=8ac82a2a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jZLHRcb.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjZLHRcb.gif&h=42707f7c&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jZLHRcb.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjZLHRcb.gif&h=42707f7c&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jZLHRcb.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjZLHRcb.gif&h=42707f7c&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jZLHRcb.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjZLHRcb.gif&h=42707f7c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/revenuetower87\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Frevenuetower87&d=QEbR3JiquQCbCEiBABctD7e6YIpo%2BX2FdnjHEpUIxFw%3D&h=5dfa521e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/revenuetower87</a> <br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/tax87\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Ftax87&d=QEbR3JiquQCbCEiBABctD7e6YIpo%2BX2FdnjHEpUIxFw%3D&h=68457ad1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/tax87</a>"},{"pid":"b228a572d9d433442881c841f2fd64a5a33ee6ad","tid":1793962,"uid":7854,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-12-22T18:23:06.000Z","msg":"呢間野以前ok<br />\n<br />\n而家好垃圾<br />\n<br />\n記得以前有個好抵食既魚生碎腩飯<br />\n<br />\n另外仲有個貴幾十蚊既升級版<br />\n<br />\n食親都話平果個無 得貴果個<br />\n<br />\n仲要好似收十點<br />\n<br />\n九點開始就打杖咁收野 都算<br />\n<br />\n仲要連拖地水都拎埋出黎拖 仲要係勁大陣味果款<br />\n<br />\n好似食緊拖地水咁 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"619a3d9882a8ad4cdf57099f00e657d6bc41c67e","tid":1793962,"uid":153880,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b228a572d9d433442881c841f2